{"tid":730522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(又嬴) 泰國13人少年足球隊被困山洞, 中國竟成最大嬴家","createTime":"2018-07-05T12:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T21:59:21.000Z","uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bba15fe3895243490eb049d2c1122d696b383a63","tid":730522,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:58:16.000Z","msg":"泰國被困洞穴13人被發現 當地指揮官:謝謝中國<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ynet.com/2018/07/05/1295109t70.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ynet.com%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F1295109t70.html&d=XPF1Hx4JootJ9ygknFWLQIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=af378d67\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ynet.com/2018/07/05/1295109t70.html</a><br />\n<br />\n泰國清萊府，一支少年足球隊被困洞穴的營救現場，中國救援隊的隊員們都進洞了，要較晚才能出來。在營地的北京平瀾公益基金會洞穴專家、救援隊隊長王英頡也一直在忙，直到4日下午3時30分，才跟記者通了電話。<br />\n<br />\n泰國方面對中、美、澳等國救援隊表示感謝，並緊接著連夜商定後續救援計劃。王英頡特意錄了一段說明會，一位當地指揮官說&ldquo;謝謝中國&rdquo;時，營地裡掌聲雷動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f9631e933248ec431bf2b1636ed949440d8f795","tid":730522,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T13:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2632e304d82bf502a49437c430e95edac3e94413","tid":730522,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T13:36:57.000Z","msg":"朱將軍都明確反共啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e67bc4de1640b1957126040ab60da1991c67a31a","tid":730522,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T17:38:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Gg3ZPJ7RJhY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGg3ZPJ7RJhY&d=XPF1Hx4JootJ9ygknFWLQIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=4e5e5f07\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu